{"tid":22350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"調查：36%中學生有「國民身分危機」　香港政策研究所倡重推國教","createTime":"2016-12-04T11:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T05:03:19.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c16f257d9944c9b84fdd18cf197721b43fd40aa8","tid":22350,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161204/s00001/1480848521268SL4_BD42553C8BF0A9447D7EF02F6AD92DC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161204%2Fs00001%2F1480848521268SL4_BD42553C8BF0A9447D7EF02F6AD92DC2.jpg&h=372f3a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港政策研究所一項調查顯示，86%被訪中學生具備香港身分認同；而具中國國民身分認同的被訪中學生達57%。研究發現，香港身分認同比國民身分顯著地高的36%中學生中，近七成從未參與遊行或以激進方式表達意見。中心認為，政府應從教育着手，解決國民身份危機。<br />\n<br />\n香港政策研究所今年5月至7月，訪問超過2000名中五學生。中心分別以7條與香港身分及中國國民身分認同有關的陳述進行調查，並將同意5條陳述或以上的人定義為擁有該身分認同。<br />\n<br />\n結果發現，具備香港人身分認同的被訪者達86%，具備中國國民身分認同的達57%，而香港身分認同較中國身分認同顯著地高的被訪者則達36%。報告將此類學生歸類為「國民身分危機學生」。<br />\n<br />\n調查指，這類學生中近七成從未參與六四集會、選舉及以遊行或更激進方式向政府表達意見。中心研究員馮智政指出，面對學生的國民身分危機，不應單靠「圈起來重點打擊」，而是應該加強國民教育。<br />\n<br />\n中心行政總裁馮可強指，有「國民身分危機」的學生不代表他們「有問題」，而是對一國兩制及社會穩定有危機，政府應該藉近期港獨議題，重推國教，加強學生對國民身分認同。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161204/s00001/1480841102628\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161204%2Fs00001%2F1480841102628&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b9b01564\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161204%2Fs00001%2F1480841102628&h=241752fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161204/s00001/1480841102628</a>"},{"pid":"7653bee89bc0cea85df10b73aa0304216bed5aad","tid":22350,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:36:14.000Z","msg":"香港身分認同較中國身分認同顯著地高的被訪者則達36%。報告將此類學生歸類為「國民身分危機學生」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f13d2178cad5bc5eefa1ef58636c48ef273ae17","tid":22350,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:39:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾親中研究所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6530d458cb49c655951dc40325ef3441332310","tid":22350,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43555b6b9513cad17ccf47212d0cb09bf352eaa","tid":22350,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cece30f45678cc2f5170d6169db78fc3ccd85c18","tid":22350,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:45:21.000Z","msg":"根據台灣經驗 推國教會衰過唔推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a71409dac99d0de3f25cae1115db9c1514859a8","tid":22350,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:47:14.000Z","msg":"老師，點解我地係中國人，局長司長個仔唔係既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a4ffbe19a91bb9b5797deb7ceeb73c56e8537c","tid":22350,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087ee5bbe5db563de3d6191cf802c854ec6fcb7d","tid":22350,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"